				  <tr>
					<td align="left" valign="top" class="art_content"><p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 23pt; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; margin-right: 0pt; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-pagination: none; mso-line-height-rule: exactly"><span style="font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt">一、基本条件</span><span style="font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 23pt; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; margin-right: 0pt; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-pagination: none; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo1"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt"><span style="mso-list: Ignore">1.</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt">遵纪守法，热爱教育事业，具有良好的思想道德素质和职业道德，身心健康。&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 23pt; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; margin-right: 0pt; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-pagination: none; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo1"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt"><span style="mso-list: Ignore">2.</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt">具有国内外高水平大学博士学位</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt">。</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 23pt; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; margin-right: 0pt; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-pagination: none; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo1"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt"><span style="mso-list: Ignore">3.</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt">具备较强的团队合作精神和独立科研能力</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt">。</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 23pt; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; margin-right: 0pt; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-pagination: none; mso-line-height-rule: exactly"><span style="font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt">二、招收方向</span><span style="font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 23pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; margin-right: 0pt; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-pagination: none; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-para-margin-top: 0.0000gd; mso-para-margin-bottom: 0.0000gd"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt">1<font face="宋体">．理论物理</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 23pt; text-indent: -7.5pt; margin: 0pt 0pt 0pt 18pt; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-pagination: none; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-para-margin-top: 0.0000gd; mso-para-margin-bottom: 0.0000gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0.0000gd; mso-char-indent-count: -1.5000"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;研究方向：凝聚态与介观理论；<font face="Times New Roman">QCD</font><font face="宋体">强作用基本理论及原子核理论；光与原子的相互作用过程及机理、量子信息。</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 23pt; margin: 0pt 0pt 0pt 8.55pt; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-pagination: none; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-para-margin-top: 0.0000gd; mso-para-margin-bottom: 0.0000gd; mso-para-margin-left: 1.7100gd"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt">&nbsp;&nbsp; 本专业领域主要专家：吴小华、</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt">岑理相、杨海棠</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt">等教授。</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 23pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; margin-right: 0pt; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-pagination: none; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-para-margin-top: 0.0000gd; mso-para-margin-bottom: 0.0000gd"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt">2<font face="宋体">．凝聚态物理</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 23pt; text-indent: -7.5pt; margin: 0pt 0pt 0pt 18pt; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-pagination: none; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-para-margin-top: 0.0000gd; mso-para-margin-bottom: 0.0000gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0.0000gd; mso-char-indent-count: -1.5000"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;研究方向：介观物理与低维电子物理；半导体材料与器件；薄膜材料与器件；辐射固体物理；光电功能材料物。</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 23pt; text-indent: -7.5pt; margin: 0pt 0pt 0pt 18pt; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-pagination: none; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-para-margin-top: 0.0000gd; mso-para-margin-bottom: 0.0000gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0.0000gd; mso-char-indent-count: -1.5000"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;本专业领域主要专家：高洁（院士）、龚敏、卢铁城</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt">、张红、贺言、Leander Schulz</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt">等教授。</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 23pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; margin-right: 0pt; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-pagination: none; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-para-margin-top: 0.0000gd; mso-para-margin-bottom: 0.0000gd"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt">3<font face="宋体">．光学</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
