<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 23pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; margin-right: 0pt; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-pagination: none; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-para-margin-top: 0.0000gd; mso-para-margin-bottom: 0.0000gd"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt">4<font face="宋体">．原子与分子物理</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 23pt; margin: 0pt 0pt 0pt 8.55pt; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-pagination: none; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-para-margin-top: 0.0000gd; mso-para-margin-bottom: 0.0000gd; mso-para-margin-left: 1.7100gd"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt">研究方向：高温高压下原子分子相互作用及状态方程；分子结构与分子激发态；外场作用下的分子结构与相互作用；电子与原子分子碰撞；光与原子分子相互作用；凝聚物质中分子结构与物性</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 23pt; margin: 0pt 0pt 0pt 8.55pt; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-pagination: none; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-para-margin-top: 0.0000gd; mso-para-margin-bottom: 0.0000gd; mso-para-margin-left: 1.7100gd"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt">本专业领域主要专家：余睽、蒋刚、程新路、陈向荣、邝小渝等教授</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
