<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 23pt; margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 7.5pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; margin-right: 0pt; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-pagination: none; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-para-margin-top: 0.0000gd; mso-para-margin-bottom: 0.0000gd; mso-char-indent-count: 1.5000"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt">&nbsp;本专业领域主要专家：安竹、徐家云</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt">、杨朝文</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt">等教授</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
