<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 23pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; margin-right: 0pt; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-pagination: none; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-para-margin-top: 0.0000gd; mso-para-margin-bottom: 0.0000gd"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt">7<font face="宋体">．高压科学与技术</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 23pt; margin: 0pt 0pt 0pt 8.55pt; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-pagination: none; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-para-margin-top: 0.0000gd; mso-para-margin-bottom: 0.0000gd; mso-para-margin-left: 1.7100gd"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt">研究方向：</span><span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体">高压下新型超硬材料的合成、表征与应用</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt">；</span><span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体">高压下金属及半导体熔体的凝固与晶体生长</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt">；</span><span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体">大腔体静高压技术的发展与相关问题研究</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt">；</span><span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体">高压下凝聚态物质弹性模量及强度的测定</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt">；</span><span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体">高压下新型能源材料与纳米材料的制备</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt">；</span><span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体">材料的高压物理</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt">；</span><span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体">高压下的原子、分子相互作用研究</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 23pt; margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 7.5pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; margin-right: 0pt; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-pagination: none; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-para-margin-top: 0.0000gd; mso-para-margin-bottom: 0.0000gd; mso-char-indent-count: 1.5000"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt">本专业领域主要专家：贺端威、杨向东、陈向荣等教授</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 23pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; margin-right: 0pt; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-pagination: none; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo2; mso-para-margin-top: 0.0000gd; mso-para-margin-bottom: 0.0000gd"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt"><span style="mso-list: Ignore">8.<span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt">等离子体物理</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 23pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; margin-right: 0pt; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-pagination: none; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-para-margin-top: 0.0000gd; mso-para-margin-bottom: 0.0000gd"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt">研究方向：束、等离子体与波的相互作用研究，包括传输与辐射的研究；磁约&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 23pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; margin-right: 0pt; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-pagination: none; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-para-margin-top: 0.0000gd; mso-para-margin-bottom: 0.0000gd"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt">&nbsp;&nbsp;束聚变等离子体理论与模拟研究，包括波驱动物理及其对磁流体不稳定性的控</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 23pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; margin-right: 0pt; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-pagination: none; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-para-margin-top: 0.0000gd; mso-para-margin-bottom: 0.0000gd"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt">&nbsp;&nbsp;制</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 23pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; margin-right: 0pt; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-pagination: none; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-para-margin-top: 0.0000gd; mso-para-margin-bottom: 0.0000gd"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt">&nbsp;&nbsp;本专业领域主要专家：唐昌建等教授</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 23pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; margin-right: 0pt; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-pagination: none; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo2; mso-para-margin-top: 0.0000gd; mso-para-margin-bottom: 0.0000gd"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt"><span style="mso-list: Ignore">9.<span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt">无线电物理</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 23pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; margin-right: 0pt; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-pagination: none; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-para-margin-top: 0.0000gd; mso-para-margin-bottom: 0.0000gd"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt">研究方向：微波系统工程；微波与复杂媒质相互作用；计算电磁学等。</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 23pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; margin-right: 0pt; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-pagination: none; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-para-margin-top: 0.0000gd; mso-para-margin-bottom: 0.0000gd"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt">&nbsp;&nbsp;本专业领域主要专家：黄卡玛、陈星、刘长军等教授</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 23pt; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; margin-right: 0pt; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-pagination: none; mso-line-height-rule: exactly"><span style="font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt">三、招收名额及时间</span><span style="font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 23pt; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; margin-right: 0pt; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-pagination: none; mso-line-height-rule: exactly"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;1<font face="宋体">、招收名额：若干</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 23pt; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; margin-right: 0pt; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-pagination: none; mso-line-height-rule: exactly"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2<font face="宋体">、招收时间：即日起</font><font face="Times New Roman">-2015</font><font face="宋体">年</font><font face="Times New Roman">10</font><font face="宋体">月</font><font face="Times New Roman">31</font><font face="宋体">日</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 23pt; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; margin-right: 0pt; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-pagination: none; mso-line-height-rule: exactly"><span style="font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt">四、应聘方式</span><span style="font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 23pt; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; margin-right: 0pt; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-pagination: none; mso-line-height-rule: exactly"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;1<font face="宋体">、应聘者将个人简历（含个人信息、教育或工作经历、奖励荣誉、参加科研项目情况、发明专利、参与发表</font><font face="Times New Roman">SCI</font><font face="宋体">论文列表及</font><font face="Times New Roman">3</font><font face="宋体">封推荐信）发送至招聘邮箱，邮件标题注明&ldquo;博士后&mdash;&mdash;</font><font face="Times New Roman">***</font><font face="宋体">（专业方向）&rdquo;。特别说明：应聘者对个人简历中所有信息的真实性负责。</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 23pt; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; margin-right: 0pt; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-pagination: none; mso-line-height-rule: exactly"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2<font face="宋体">、流动站初审材料后，提交给相关导师，由导师组织面试。</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 23pt; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; margin-right: 0pt; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-pagination: none; mso-line-height-rule: exactly"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;3<font face="宋体">、通过面试的博士后候选人在四川大学人事信息管理系统（</font><font face="Times New Roman"><a href="http://rsxxgl.scu.edu.cn/Common/Recruitment.aspx">http://rsxxgl.scu.edu.cn/Common/Recruitment.aspx</a></font><font face="宋体">）填报应聘申请，审核通过后，在中国博士后网站（</font><font face="Times New Roman"><a href="http://www.chinapostdoctor.org.cn">www.chinapostdoctor.org.cn</a></font><font face="宋体">）提交申请，具体操作流程及注意事项见四川大学人事处网站（</font><font face="Times New Roman"><a href="http://rsc.scu.edu.cn/NewsClass.aspx?NewsClassId=12">http://rsc.scu.edu.cn/</a></font><font face="宋体">）博士后栏目。</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 23pt; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; margin-right: 0pt; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-pagination: none; mso-line-height-rule: exactly"><span style="font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt">五、岗位待遇</span><span style="font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 23pt; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; margin-right: 0pt; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-pagination: none; mso-line-height-rule: exactly"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;1<font face="宋体">、&nbsp;学校为统招博士后提供薪酬约</font><font face="Times New Roman">12</font><font face="宋体">万元</font><font face="Times New Roman">/</font><font face="宋体">年（税前），外籍博士后提供薪酬约</font><font face="Times New Roman">15</font><font face="宋体">万元</font><font face="Times New Roman">/</font><font face="宋体">年（税前），为符合条件的博士后提供校内博士后公寓租住，每套公寓配备有基本家具和燃气用具。</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 23pt; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; margin-right: 0pt; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-pagination: none; mso-line-height-rule: exactly"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2<font face="宋体">、部分学科合作导师为博士后另提供额外酬金，详讯导师。</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 23pt; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; margin-right: 0pt; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-pagination: none; mso-line-height-rule: exactly"><span style="font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt">六、联系方式</span><span style="font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 23pt; text-indent: 21pt; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; margin-right: 0pt; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-pagination: none; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0000"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt">联系人：袁老师、吴老师&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 23pt; text-indent: 21pt; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; margin-right: 0pt; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-pagination: none; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0000"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt">联系电话：<font face="Times New Roman">85412323</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 23pt; text-indent: 21pt; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; margin-right: 0pt; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-pagination: none; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0000"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt">邮箱：<font face="Times New Roman">physics@scu.edu.cn</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 23pt; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; margin-right: 0pt; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-pagination: none; mso-line-height-rule: exactly"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: right; line-height: 23pt; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; margin-right: 0pt; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-pagination: none; mso-line-height-rule: exactly"><span style="font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt">&nbsp; 四川大学物理学博士后流动站</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: right; line-height: 23pt; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; margin-right: 0pt; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-pagination: none; mso-line-height-rule: exactly"><span style="font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt">2015年5月</span><span style="font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 23pt; text-autospace: ideograph-numeric; margin-right: 0pt; mso-para-margin-right: 0.0000gd; mso-pagination: none; mso-line-height-rule: exactly"><span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
